sources.title: 1961 Thriller | Callaghan is back | French film directed by Willy Rozier | with Tony Wright
sources.description:
Slim Callaghan investigates the theft of the famous Upper Sangha diamonds. Disguised as an auxiliary of the `Salvation Army', he approaches a luxurious yacht where a drag party is being organized. During a trick of illusionism, Callaghan manages to steal the precious diamonds, but the thief escapes.

Original title: Callaghan remet ça (1961)

Written & Directed by: Willy Rozier

Main Cast
Anthony 'Tony' Wright – Slim Callaghan
Geneviève Kervine – Carola
André Luguet – Nick
Fabienne Dali – Maguy
Nicolas Vogel – Morand

Release Date: April 5, 1961 
Filming Location: France

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/29M-P2EF3jw
